-- Vestas May Tap Investors, Customers to Fund Parks, Borsen Says
-- B y   F r a n c e s   S c h w a r t z k o p f f
-- 2012-01-16T07:30:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-16/vestas-may-tap-investors-customers-to-fund-wind-parks-borsen-says.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S (VWS)  is
considering tapping institutional investors and customers to
invest in large off-shore wind parks that require substantial
capital, Borsen reported, citing Chief Executive Officer  Ditlev
Engel .  Vestas has gotten many questions from customers and others
and, because the parks require a large investment, the company
is investigating the idea, the Copenhagen-based newspaper quoted
the CEO as saying.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
